NOTICE — Multiaxial Diagnostic Expert System
=============================================

NOT A MEDICAL DEVICE / KEIN MEDIZINPRODUKT
------------------------------------------

This software is NOT a medical device within the meaning of the EU
Medical Device Regulation (MDR) 2017/745 nor the In-Vitro Diagnostic
Regulation (IVDR) 2017/746. It is:

- NOT clinically validated
- NOT reviewed or certified by BfArM, any Notified Body, or any
  other competent authority
- NOT a clinical decision support system in the regulatory sense
- NOT intended for diagnosis, prevention, monitoring, prediction,
  prognosis, treatment, or alleviation of disease

It is a software prototype for research, teaching, and software
engineering purposes. It explores the structured documentation and
coding of diagnostic reasoning across a 6-axis model integrating
DSM-5-TR, ICD-11, and ICF.

