NO DIAGNOSIS, NO THERAPY RECOMMENDATION /
KEINE DIAGNOSE, KEINE THERAPIEEMPFEHLUNG
----------------------------------------

Outputs of this software are structured coding proposals and
pattern-based notifications. They are:

- NOT clinical diagnoses
- NOT therapy recommendations
- NOT a substitute for clinical assessment by qualified
  professionals

Diagnosis, treatment decisions, and clinical responsibility remain
with qualified professionals (physicians, psychotherapists) in
accordance with applicable professional law (e.g. § 76 SGB V,
§ 630a BGB in Germany).

